onathan Frakes]]\n|[[William Riker]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n|[[Thomas Riker]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}{{Efn-lg|Jonathan Frakes appeared in \"[[Defiant (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|Defiant]]\" as Lt. Thomas Riker.}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[LeVar Burton]]\n|[[Geordi La Forge]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Denise Crosby]]\n|[[Tasha Yar]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Denise Crosby left the cast of the ''Next Generation'' in \"[[Skin of Evil]]\". She appearanced as Tasha Yar in \"[[Yesterday's Enterprise]]\" and \"[[All Good Things... (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|All Good Things...]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Sela (Star Trek)|Sela]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Michael Dorn]]\n|[[Worf]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Michael Dorn joined the cast of ''Deep Space Nine'' in \"[[The Way of the Warrior (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|The Way of the Warrior]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Gates McFadden]]\n|[[Beverly Crusher]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Gates McFadden was replaced by [[Diana Muldaur]] as the ship's doctor for Season 2 of the ''Next Generation''.}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Marina Sirtis]]\n|[[Deanna Troi]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Brent Spiner]]\n|[[Data (Star Trek)|Data]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}{{Efn-lg|Brent Spiner made an uncredited voice cameo in \"These Are the Voyages...\".}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest