ark]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Alexander Siddig]]{{Efn-lg|Alexander Siddig was billed Siddig el Fadil from 1993 to 1995, and for his guest appearance on the ''Next Generation''.}}\n|[[Julian Bashir]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Nana Visitor]]\n|[[Kira Nerys]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Kate Mulgrew]]\n|[[Kathryn Janeway]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Robert Beltran]]\n|[[Chakotay]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Roxann Dawson]]\n|[[B'Elanna Torres]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Jennifer Lien]]\n|[[Kes (Star Trek)|Kes]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Jennifer Lien left the cast of ''Voyager'' in \"[[The Gift (Star Trek: Voyager)|The Gift]]\", but made a guest appearance in \"[[Fury (Star Trek: Voyager)|Fury]]\"}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Robert Duncan McNeill]]\n|[[Tom Paris]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Ethan Phillips]]\n|[[Neelix]]\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Robert Picardo]]\n|[[The Doctor (Star Trek: Voyager)|The Doctor]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}{{Efn-lg|Robert Picardo appeared in ''Deep Space Nine'' Emergency Medical Hologram in \"[[Doctor Bashir, I Presume?]]\".}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Tim Russ]]\n|[[Tuvok]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}{{Efn-lg|Tim Russ appeared in \"[[Through the Looking Glass (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|Through the Looking Glass]]\" as the [[Mirror Universe]] analogue of Tuvok.}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Jeri Ryan]]\n|[[Seven of Nine]]\n| co